External knowledge: 
- Featured blog posts refer to blog posts with the 'featured' type, which indicates that they are highlighted or prioritized;
- User roles are the categories or groups that users belong to, such as 'content manager', 'editor', or 'admin';
- Interactions refer to the total number of times users interact with the featured blog posts, which may include likes, comments, shares, etc.
